            </div>
            <script>
              document.getElementById('basicsModal7-content6').innerHTML =
                marked('<hr />*Listening to different stories from different perspectives of the similar experiences in similar spaces helps provide the basis for the analysis we must do. As the analysis, and the conclusions from that analysis, is based on our selection of stories, it is important to get a broad coverage of the stories from different perspectives.*');
            </script>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row text-left">
          <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-7 col-sm-push-5 col-md-8 col-md-push-4">
