            </div>
            <script>
              document.getElementById('basicsModal7-content8').innerHTML =
                marked('<hr />*Assuming we have some understanding of the problems within a particular space, chances are someone else has done similar work with similar problems in the past. Our work is often built on the shoulders of giants before us, and modern media such as the internet has made it increasingly possible to search for similar analysis, which we then use as examples for our own analysis.*');
            </script>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row text-left">
